devdoc.details: A decentralized health records management system Stores metadata and IPFS pointers on-chain, actual health data on IPFS

params._ipfsHash: IPFS hash where encrypted health data is stored

returns._0: recordId The ID of the newly created record

addRecordByProvider(address,string,uint8.details: Add a record issued by a healthcare provider

params._ipfsHash: IPFS hash of the encrypted data

params._recordId: ID of the record to delete

getAuditLogs(uint256).details: Get audit logs for a record

getPatientRecords(address).details: Get all record IDs for a patient

getRecord(uint256).details: Get details of a specific record

getTotalRecords().details: Get total number of records in the system

grantAccess(address,uint256[],uint256).details: Grant access to specific records for a healthcare provider

params._durationInDays: How many days the access should last
params._recordIds: Array of record IDs to grant access to

hasAccess(address,address,uint256).details: Check if an address has access to a specific record

params._recordId: Record ID to check access for

returns._0: bool True if access is granted

logAccess(uint256,string).details: Log access to a record (for audit trail)

revokeAccess(address).details: Revoke access from a healthcare provider

setEmergencyContact(address).details: Set emergency contact who can access all records

updateRecord(uint256,string,string).details: Update an existing record (creates a new version)

params._recordId: ID of the record to update
